<div id="review_1241185321" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1241185321" />
    <a title="Amy Manemann" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6087971-amy-manemann"><img alt="Amy Manemann" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442601099p2/6087971.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1241185321?book_show_action=true">Mar 30, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amy Manemann" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amy Manemann" href="/user/show/6087971-amy-manemann">Amy Manemann</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1241185321" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16170809967011047904">Poignant and heart wrenching, Author Stacy Eaton gives us a peek into the dark world of Domestic Abuse with her newest release. In Barbara&apos;s Plea, we are taken down the dark path of Barbara Murphy, the wife of a prominent lawyer who abuses her on a daily basis. With the help of some friends, Barbara is able to escape with her daughter and return to her roots in her Grandmother&apos;s home where she connects with her Grandmother&apos;s new tenant, a woodworker named Greyson Bloodstone. One look into Barbar</span>
  <span id="freeText16170809967011047904" style="display:none">Poignant and heart wrenching, Author Stacy Eaton gives us a peek into the dark world of Domestic Abuse with her newest release. In Barbara's Plea, we are taken down the dark path of Barbara Murphy, the wife of a prominent lawyer who abuses her on a daily basis. With the help of some friends, Barbara is able to escape with her daughter and return to her roots in her Grandmother's home where she connects with her Grandmother's new tenant, a woodworker named Greyson Bloodstone. One look into Barbara and Allie's fearful eyes, and Grey is a goner for the fleeing duo. This story was heart-wrenching, to say the very least. As always, Stacy Eaton's writing is heartfelt, knowledgeable, and helps you to understand a world you may know nothing about. I certainly didn't. For those who have lived through it, and for those who are still living it, my heart truly goes out to you. An excellent read you won't want to miss. </span>
  <a data-text-id="16170809967011047904" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


