<span id="freeTextContainer4691147524287519596"><strong>Wow!! Such a powerful read!! </strong><br/><br/>I don&apos;t know how Stacy Eaton does it, but her writing is so powerful, so meaningful, and will take your breath away. <br/><br/>Writing about domestic violence is very hard to do, but to do so in such a realistic and awe-inspiring manner takes a lot of skill and understanding of the topic. <br/><br/>This novel is so meaningful and so well written. It packs a huge punch (no pun intended), that just resonates with the reader immediately and never lets go. <br/><br/>An absolutely amazing read... Pick</span>
  <span id="freeText4691147524287519596" style="display:none"><strong>Wow!! Such a powerful read!! </strong><br /><br />I don't know how Stacy Eaton does it, but her writing is so powerful, so meaningful, and will take your breath away. <br /><br />Writing about domestic violence is very hard to do, but to do so in such a realistic and awe-inspiring manner takes a lot of skill and understanding of the topic. <br /><br />This novel is so meaningful and so well written. It packs a huge punch (no pun intended), that just resonates with the reader immediately and never lets go. <br /><br />An absolutely amazing read... Pick it up asap. Better than a 5* read</span>
